your emotions.

00:21:31.458 --> 00:21:33.626 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA]
Guess we don't, huh?

00:21:37.255 --> 00:21:39.591 position:50% align:center
[CHACHA] You've got to
watch this soap with me!

00:21:39.674 --> 00:21:41.926 position:50% align:center
--I'm obsessed! No excuses!
--What? Hey, no pushing me!

00:21:42.010 --> 00:21:43.219 position:50% align:center
Let's go!

00:21:46.306 --> 00:21:48.391 position:50% align:center
