actually confirmed that yet.

00:22:00.362 --> 00:22:02.072 position:50% align:center
Yes. Of course.

00:22:02.155 --> 00:22:03.281 position:50% align:center
Thank you.

00:22:04.616 --> 00:22:07.619 position:50% align:center
Wow. That was something.

00:22:07.702 --> 00:22:09.954 position:50% align:center
Sounds like our
uber-conservative Tokyo branch

00:22:10.038 --> 00:22:12.999 position:50% align:center
